c, usually assumed in the\nliterature, is close to the optimal provided that the threshold distance is\ncarefully chosen.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Jul 2012 16:28:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-07-27"}
