ov type D.\nFinally, we make contact between the semiclassical asymptotic behaviour of the\nmodel and our construction, clarifying the relation of the Regge geometries\nwith the original phase space.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Jul 2012 17:48:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 27 Sep 2012 10:31:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-05"}
